only candidate that meets the reliability requirement outright, and the other candidates lack comparable evidence of reliability.\nTherefore, based on the available attributes, **Candidate\u202fB** appears to be the strongest overall fit for a high\u2011responsibility, long\u2011distance pilot role.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_2\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
